article_id:1124,category_name:News,title_name:Issue Regarding Sword Force Strike Power [Update],image_path:,message:<div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Update <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1583233200"></span>]</strong></span><br>This issue was resolved with the data update applied on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1583233200"></span>.<br><br>As a token of our appreciation for your patience, we are sending a gift of 150 wyrmite to all players who started playing before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1583233200"></span>.<br>This gift can be claimed from your goodie box for up to 7 days after reception.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><div><br></div><hr><div>We have confirmed an issue where the damage dealt by sword users&#39; force strikes is lower than expected following the data update that was applied on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1583213400"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>We are currently investigating this issue.</div><div>Any further updates will be added to this notice.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1583223900,update_time1583381614